title: Longmire
description: Walt Longmire is the dedicated and unflappable sheriff of Absaroka County, Wyoming. Widowed only a year, he is a man in psychic repair but buries his pain behind his brave face, unassuming grin and dry wit.

title: The Legend of Korra
description: Avatar Korra fights to keep Republic City safe from the evil forces of both the physical and spiritual worlds.

title: Continuum
description: A City Protective Services (CPS) agent from the year 2077 finds herself trapped in present-day Vancouver and searching for ruthless criminals from the future.

title: Sword Art Online
description: In the year 2022, thousands of people get trapped in a new virtual MMORPG and the lone wolf player, Kirito, works to escape.

title: High School DxD
description: After being killed on his first date, idiotic and perverted Issei Hyodo is resurrected as a demon by Rias Gremory only to be recruited into her club of high-class devils.

title: Kingdom
description: In ancient China, a young boy dreams of becoming the greatest general of the Qin Kingdom.

title: Lab Rats
description: A scrawny 14-year-old, having discovered his inventor stepdad has three bionic, super-powered teens living cloistered in a secret lab beneath their home, brings them out into the world.

title: The Firm
description: Defense Attorney Mitch McDeere is targeted for execution by the Chicago Mob in retaliation for bringing down a profitable Mob-operated Memphis law firm ten years earlier.

title: Ultimate Spider-Man
description: Spider-Man battles evil with a new team of teen colleagues and training from S.H.I.E.L.D.

title: Medaka Box
description: Medaka, elected student council president, introduces a suggestion box to help fellow students. However, some submissions pose tough challenges for her and her friends.

title: Alcatraz
description: In 1963, all the prisoners and guards mysteriously disappear from Alcatraz. In the present day, they resurface and a secret agency is tasked with re-capturing them.

title: MrBeast
description: Philanthropist and entrepreneur Jimmy Donaldson, better known as MrBeast, and his group of friends do stunts and challenges that no one else dares to try.

title: Tron: Uprising
description: In the computer world of the Grid, a young program joins Tron's fight against their world's tyranny.

title: Video Game High School
description: In a futuristic world where gaming is the top sport, a teenager attends a school which specializes in a curriculum of video games in each genre.

title: The River
description: The crew of a research vessel are on a quest to find a missing TV explorer in the Amazon.

title: Treasure Island
description: In 1765, young English boy Jim Hawkins gets involved with buccaneers during his quest to find pirate Captain Flint's treasure buried on a secret island.

title: Space Battleship Yamato 2199
description: In the year 2199, the space battleship Yamato embarks on a voyage to the planet Iscandar, to retrieve a device that will rejuvenate a war-ravaged Earth.

title: Missing
description: When a woman's son goes missing under suspicious circumstances, she will do anything it takes to find him.

title: Jormungand
description: A group of cheerful friends who help Koko avoid trouble. However, charming life comes to an end when they discover that Koko is an arms dealer, and that her happy bodyguards are elite soldiers who are "the best of the best" at something.

title: Gon
description: The Gon series features the adventures of the irascible title character, a tiny fictional dinosaur, as he interacts with the natural world. Gon somehow survived the extinction of his fellow dinosaurs and interacts with paleolithic animals.

title: Queen's Blade: Rebellion
description: The story is set four years after the first story-line and revolves around Annelotte, the rebelling knight princess who stands up to the tyranny of the new queen.

title: The King 2 Hearts
description: The crown-prince of South Korea is forced to work alongside a female North Korean military officer. Political and emotional complications lead to an uneasy marriage engagement.

title: Level Up
description: A group of teens fight video game creatures in the real world.

title: Zetman
description: Jin and Kouga may come from very different walks of life, but both boys are searching for the real meaning of justice and what it means to be a hero.

title: Smile PreCure!
description: Once upon a time, there was a kingdom of fairy tales called "Märchenland", where many fairy tale characters live together in joy. Suddenly, the evil emperor Pierrot made an invasion on Märchenland, sealing its Queen in the process. To revive the Queen, the symbol of happiness called Cure Decor, "the Queen's scattered power of light of happiness", is required. To collect the Cure Decor, a fairy named Candy searches for the Pretty Cures on Earth. There, Candy meets a girl, who decides to collect the Cure Decor. Now, will the world earn a "happy ending"?

title: Accel World
description: Haruyuki is an overweight kid and at bottom of food chain at his middle school. Within sci-fi setting of real world he often seeks refuge in a virtual one.

title: The High Fructose Adventures of Annoying Orange
description: Orange goes on adventures with his friends. His strange friend Nerville, basically played by a YouTuber, is afraid of aliens. So Orange and his friends are the ones who can stop the adventure.

title: Uncanny X-Men
description: A low-budget adaptation of the popular superhero comic book series.

title: Blackout
description: A team of mercenaries lead by a disgraced former Marine causes a blackout in Los Angeles to gain access to some CIA slush funds.

title: Moordvrouw
description: In a Frisian town in the Netherlands, a police team solves crimes, led by chief Carla Vreeswijk.

title: Naruto SD: Rock Lee & His Ninja Pals
description: Naruto SD: Rock Lee & His Ninja Pals is story of Rock Lee's adventures from Rock Lee's perspective.
originalTitle: Naruto SD: Rokku Rî no seishun Furu Pawâ ninden

title: Flint
description: An ex soldier comes to visit a military friend and finds trouble right away. It all starts with a rape of a girl by the local thugs in the town. He must use his fighting skills to defeat the thugs.

title: Seinto Seiya: Omega
description: After many years since the last battle, Mars, the god of war, resurrect and wants to dominate earth again. The new generation of saint soldiers join together to fight against newly emerged dark forces.

title: Lagrange: The Flower of Rin-ne
description: Madoka an energetic school girl is recruited by a mysterious girl called Lan to pilot a robot in order to protect her city from enemies from space with an as of yet unknown goal.

title: King David
description: The story of "David" anointed as a young man to be king of Israel, an action that would give him a turbulent life until his reign was secured. Based upon the text of books of "Samuel".

title: Fearless Heart
description: Born to a life of privilege, Camila embarks on a journey of self-discovery after tragedy strikes. Navigating love, loss, and intrigue, she finds her fearless heart amidst unexpected alliances and betrayals.

title: Tight-Rope
description: A love relationship between the reluctant heir of a yakuza family and his childhood friend, that started budding in their school days and keeps developing slowly but surely.

title: Limbo
description: Limbo follows the lives of four best friends: Ask, Boye, Louise and Naya. As they deal with the challenges of going from kids to adults.

title: Motorcity
description: A fictitious futuristic Detroit, which is an elevated metropolis built over the old Detroit, classified as Detroit Deluxe. It is owned by evil billionaire Abraham Kane.

title: Walang hanggan
description:
Cruz sisters Virginia (Susan Roces) and Margaret (Helen Gamboa) vie for the love of Joseph Montenegro (Eddie Garcia) in the fictional province of Olivarez. Virginia had to sacrifice everything to let Margaret live a better life with Joseph. Around two decades later, Margaret and Joseph's son Marco (Richard Gomez) develops feelings for Emily Cardenas (Dawn Zulueta), a daughter of a worker in their plantation. However, numerous circumstances and Margaret's haughtiness towards Emily prompts Marco to marry rich banker Jane Bonifacio (Rita Avila) much to Emily's detriment. It fuels the Virginia-Margaret rivalry more, especially when Marco migrates to the US after Emily shuns him when he tries to explain.

Meanwhile, laborer William Alcantara (Joel Torre) settle in Olivarez with his children Katerina (Julia Montes) and Tomas (Joem Bascon). He adopts a streetboy named Daniel (Coco Martin) while working at the Cruz family business, where Virginia assumes a role as his adoptive grandmother. Daniel first plays around with Katerina but they gradually develop a friendship over the next several years. Marco and Jane return home with their children Johanna (Melissa Ricks) and Nathan (Paulo Avelino), with the latter becoming interested in Katerina as well. Virginia and Margaret's rivalry affects the children. Emily reemerges with a plan to avenge her woes by taking all the shares in the business. At the same time, Nathan schemes to get Daniel out of the way so he can marry Katerina. After Tomas stabs Daniel, Emily saves him and they escape to live in Italy as Emily and Daniel Guidotti. Emily uses Daniel to take revenge on the Montenegros. Later, Emily shows herself as Emily Guidotti. Soon she's in competition with the Montenegros. Miguel Ramos (Noni Buencamino) a person working for Emily loves her and decides to hide the truth from Emily (Daniel is the son of Emily). Long later, Emily and Marco find out the truth and get married. In the end, Daniel and Katerina dies.

title: Total Drama Revenge of the Island
description: Teens vs each other in a mock off cartoon reality show. All about the fight to win, no matter what.

title: Beyblade: Shogun Steel
description: A new era of Beyblade has begun, bringing with it new Blades. Zyro, champion of his hometown, heads to Metal Bey City to find greater opponents. He'll test his might against the Cyclone Stadium, and discover how to become a true Blader.

title: Bridal Mask
description: In 1930s Korea, during the Japanese colonial era, a man who is a Korean police officer assigned to aid the Japanese in the annihilation of the local rebellion, secretly dons the 'Bridal Mask' and fights the unjust regime.

title: Komisarz Alex
description: Komisarz Alex is a Polish murder mystery drama.A police team solves murder cases with the help of the police dog Alex.Each Episode has a different murder case but all episodes are linked.

title: Hikonin Sentai Akibaranger
description: In a world where delusions become reality, three strange heroes must battle the evil Malshina, protect the world of Super Sentai, keep the show from being cancelled, and most importantly, become an official Sentai team.

title: Acayip Hikayeler
description: Turkish television series adapted from Galip Tekin's fantastic story line.

title: La fuga
description: Daniel is a young idealist and active member of a revolutionary movement called the Resistance. He is arrested and taken to La Torre, an oil platform in the middle of the ocean, converted into a maximum security prison.

title: Conspiracy 365
description: Callum Ormond, a 15 year old who is forced to become a fugitive as he searches for the truth behind the death of a family member.

title: Lupin the Third: The Woman Called Fujiko Mine
description: The story of how the fashionable femme fatale Fujiko Mine first met Lupin III, her sometimes-lover and sometimes-rival, and the rest of his gang.
originalTitle: Lupin the Third: Mine Fujiko to iu onna

title: The Witches of Calenda
description: The judge named Sara has moved to Calenda, along with her teenage daughter, Leire. Her plan to rebuild the family life has been spoiled when her husband disappears. This will be the first of a series of shocking events that will convince the judge that Calenda is not the peaceful place as it seemed to be.

title: Nyaruko: Crawling with Love
description: Actual H.P. Lovecraft's alien god of chaos from Cthulhu Mythos appears to a high school boy in the form of a whimsical girl Nyaruko claiming that it's there to protect him from other alien godlike races who want to abduct him.

title: Black Rock Shooter
description: On first day of junior high school, Mato Kuroi happens to run into Yomi Takanashi.

title: Bad Days
description: Even heroes wake up on the wrong side of the bed. This show features our greatest heroes and their greatest failures.

title: Tree Fu Tom
description: A boy goes to the woods behind his house and enters a magical world, where he becomes a superhero.

title: Tokumei Sentai Go-Busters
description: In the year Neo AD 2012 the city runs on massive energy source enetron The Go-Busters young Spy's fight to it and innocent people from the evil Vaglass.

title: Dragon Force
description: The earth's environment will deteriorate, and mankind will fall into a major ecological crisis. The Forestry Bureau, the Bureau of Land and Resources and other relevant departments attach great importance to them.

title: Space Girl
description: The various adventures of Space Girl, an outer space heroine who deals with aliens, mad scientists, and other space things.

title: Kaijudo: Rise of the Duel Masters
description: The series follows the adventures of a young boy named Rai who possesses the rare ability to befriend and duel alongside fantastical creatures from a parallel dimension.

title: Lynch
description: Jerónimo Lynch, owner of the "Lynch Funeral Home", is about to be arrested and accepts Isabel Reyes' offer to stage his death. This leads to the setting up of an enterprise staging the death of people who wish to take on a new identity.

title: The Good Daughter
description: Bea seems to have the perfect life-having a family who adores and provides her every need - until a woman named Sharon and her 10-year old daughter Julia appear at her 18th birthday party and introduce themselves as her father's second family. Distraught, Bea's mother Tina leaves the venue of the party in tears and unfortunately meets an accident when an explosion takes place in the building, which also puts at risk Sharon and Julia. While Tina agonizes in pain, Sharon sees this as an opportunity to replace the former in Rico's life leading her to kill Tina. As Bea weeps for her mother's demise, she puts the blame on her father, who is then being pressured by Sharon to marry her or else she and her daughter will leave thecountry for good. Rico, torn between Bea's disapproval and the possibility of building a new family with Sharon, eventually gives in to Sharon's demands. As Sharon assumes the role of Rico's new wife, her true colors further surface as she mistreats Bea behind Rico's back. Feeling helpless and alone more than ever, Bea runs away from home and travels to her grandmother's province. However, as Bea begins to find comfort in the arms of her Lola Lourdes , she discovers that her father is gravely ill and that Sharon has started to take over the company. More than that, she uncovers more of her stepmother's evil deeds, including the real reason why her mother died, prompting her to return home and reunite with her father. As she comes to face with the woman who has done her family wrong, how will Bea protect her father and the business that is also rightfully hers? Can peace still be restored in a home that was once shattered by dishonesty and spite?

title: Krew z krwi
description: After the death of her gangster husband, Carmen is forced to take over his business and fight for her family's safety

title: Proper Manors
description: Proper Manors is a soap opera about a group of recently graduated teenagers in the small town of Proper, USA. They begin to discover that they are all merely pawns in the games that the adults of Proper play.

title: Upotte!!
description: Girls personifying assault rifles embark on fun adventures while providing accurate firearm facts.

title: Brave 10
description: A girl being pursued by assassins runs into a ronin samurai. He saves her and subsequently can't get rid of her, as she begs for him to escort her to a nearby castle.

title: Aquarion EVOL
description: Residents of planet Vega fight off invaders from Altair. Amata Sora, a young man with flight abilities, befriends Mikono Suzushiro. They join Neo-DEAVA and pilot Aquaria robots alongside other gifted Elements to counter Altairian attacks.

title: Holy Land
description: Kang Yoo is a socially awkward boy who is constantly bullied by others. Having Taught himself the basic of boxing from a book, He defends himself from a thug and is started to be called 'The Hunter' by the thugs in the streets. Soon he meets with Sang Ho, a former boxing champion and he becomes his mentor.

title: Senki Zesshô Shinfogia
description: Tsubasa Kazanari and Kanade Amou-the idol duo known as Zwei Wing, use their songs to power ancient weapons known as "Symphogears" to combat a deadly alien race called the "Noise." While the general public is aware of the Noise's existence, knowledge of the Symphogears are kept a secret. When the Noise attack one of Zwei Wing's concerts, Kanade sacrifices herself to protect a young girl named Hibiki Tachibana, leaving Tsubasa devastated and a fragment of her Symphogear embedded within Hibiki. Two years pass and Hibiki is once again dragged into a Noise attack. While rescuing a young girl who has been left behind during the evacuation, she awakens the power of Kanade's Symphogear lying within her. Although Tsubasa still grieves over the loss of Kanade, both girls must now learn to work together using their powers to defend humanity against the Noise.

title: Hit Boys
description: When these two brothers join up with the town's biggest crime boss, the boys think they're on their way to the big time, but instead, find themselves in big time trouble.

title: Fight Night Legacy
description: When former boxer and ex-con Andre Johnson discovers that his health is failing, he returns home to rebuild the life he left behind, but gets an opportunity to build a future and a family.

title: The Proxy
description: An evil organisation that creates superpowered reanimated humans known as Proxies want to recover a flash drive contains secret data from Ashens, his neighbour Tom and a unique Proxy.

title: Eureka Seven: Ao
description: In a technologically advanced future, a young boy accidentally activates the strange giant robot his mother piloted before she went missing. He becomes a pilot with only one mission - to find his mother.

title: Top Guns
description: Games show where contestants complete marksmen related tasks to eventually be crowned top shot

title: The Chaser
description: Detective Baek Hong-Suk investigates his daughter's death, uncovering a conspiracy. Reporter Seo Ji-Won, daughter of a corporate tycoon, aids him while battling conflict as her brother-in-law, politician, is implicated in corruption.

title: Hero
description: Set in the year of 2020 in the fictional city of Muyoung which is full of corruption. Kim Heung Chul obtains a superhuman power by a special chance. He becomes a hero with that ability in the world where justice is gone.

title: Sea Rescue
description: An educational documentary series that showcases stories of rescue, rehabilitation and return to the wild of marine animals by a team of dedicated vets, animal care experts, animal science researchers and government authorities.

title: My Little Portal
description: Twilight Sparkle wakes up in an abandoned science lab with no memory of her past and must unite with her friends to defeat a corrupt artificial intelligence system.

title: Plastic Man
description: The misadventures of the original stretchable superhero.

title: Vibe
description: Shorts about the DC superhero Vibe competing in a break-dancing competition with his sidekick Daniel. Vibe must defeat the robot Extreme-O, created by Professor Ivo , who is disguised as the judge of the break dancing competition.

title: Shalen
description: When evil monsters invade the Earth, only a special group of chosen Wuxia warriors - all with a special mark on their hands - can save the day.

title: Kurohyou 2: Ryu Ga Gotoku Ashura-hen
description: Ukyo Tatsuya, who left behind the unprecedented record of ten consecutive wins in the underground fighting circuit called Dragon Heat, headed to Las Vegas by himself to banish his sorrow over the deaths of his older sister and good friend and made his debut in boxing. Returning to Tokyo for the first time in over a year for his pro debut in Japan, Tatsuya heads to Kamurocho where he was born and raised, but what awaits him is the underground fighting gang 'Ashura' which acts as if Kamurocho is their turf. Tatsuya meets the youngsters of Dragon Heat who are fighting back, and the nurse Aya's and his destiny change dramatically once again.

title: Crossing the Line
description: The series has four episodes, each one having its own main plot and special participation of many actors, but the same cast is present in the whole story. Actor Milhem Cortaz, know by his acting in movies such as Carandiru (2003), Tropa de Elite (2007) and Assalto ao Banco Central (2011) gives life to the story's main character, an anti-hero in the skin of officer Medeiros who has a crime to investigate and solve in each episode for which counts with a high qualified team, formed by investigator Clarice, performed by actress Rafaela Mandelli and officer Brandão, lived by actor Claudio Gabriel. Medeiros's got a not very orthodox way of solving the crimes that arrive on his hands, which causes conflicts with Clarice, with whom also has a non solved romance. Out of Control, a series with tons of action, emotion and suspense, shows the daily life of the exciting universe of police investigation. The project is a production by Gullane in coproduction with Grifa Films.

title: Star Trek: GENESIS
description: A movie about star trek with trekkians

title: The Amazing Race - Norway
description: Multiple teams from Norway race around the globe for over 1,000,000kr to 'amazing' locations.

title: Katarina's Kat Scratch Cinema
description: "Katarina's Kat Scratch Cinema" is a direct-to-dvd hosted anthology series with Katarina Severen as host.

title: Paboo & Mojies
description: Paboo is a young yet curious panda boy who lives in a magical land called Mojies Town. One day, he found a magical book up the Moji Tree and decides to get it. After he got the book, a magical fairy named Pappy popped out and told him about the book he found: The Mojires Book and also about the Magic Words that would help him and his friends in any situation. Now, Paboo and his friends all explore and solve problems in a quirky, imaginative, and sometimes zany world and discover each Magic Word with the help from Pappy.

title: Citizen
description: Agent Fleur is scared. Her partner is being chased and hunted by men in black suits. Unable to save him, she watches as he is taken down and they insert a mysterious chip into the back of his skull. Even worse, it appears the entire town is controlled by something, some hive-mind computer, turning all the citizens into soldiers against their will. Not only must she find her missing partner in this small mid-American town, but she must learn to work with a cocky, arrogant Agent Dempster who has been sent in to back her up. Will she find Agent Travis before it's too late? Will she figure out what's happening to the citizens of this perfect town and save them from an uncertain fate?

title: Geymery
description: The eight-part series continues and develops the story of Pavel Sanaev's film trilogy "On the Game". Some of the former heroes died, someone went to prison - which means that the mysterious high-ranking forces need new ideal soldiers to fulfill their anti-human plans.

title: Mulan on the Run
description: The story starts with a bomber who takes a bus hostage. Aota Pharmacy's representative in Taiwan is apprehended with a bomb while taking a bus hijack, yet dies mysteriously in jail. At the same time, suddenly, mysterious deaths start spreading over one by one. On the other hand, Japanese detective agency "5" received a request by the chairman of Aota Pharmacy. Agent 511 is asked to investigate the company's research development supervisor Taro Kishitani, who has been rumored to have created a deadly virus that can kill at once without leaving any evidence. 511's investigations show that Taro Kishitani, his lover Kumiko and his son have fled to Taiwan. Thus, 511 contacts his old friend in Taiwan, Team Mulan's supervisor - Vice Chief of police Chen Xi and requests his help in investigations. Chen Xi assigns Team Mulan to be in charged of this mission.

title: Uchastkovyy
description: Crime has always flourished in the high-rise buildings on the outskirts of the capital, in particular one block, known in slang as Novosiolki, and local residents are so used to the situation that no-one has been able to convince them that things could change. But it appears that life is about to improve with the appointment of a new district police officer, Sergey Gromov, a former senior investigator with the Homicide Department. Sergey dislikes revisiting his past, but if his previous investigations have taught him anything, it is to quickly assess a situation and make a firm decision. Sergey, however, has not been assigned to solve cold cases, instead, his primary task will be to deter criminals and prevent future offences.

title: Babble-On Begins
description: After being shunned by Hollywood, Kevin Smith and Ralph Garman don masks and take to the streets to exact revenge on the true villains of Tinsel Town. Based on the award winning podcast, Hollywood Babble-On.

title: Kamen Rider X Super Sentai: Super Hero Taihen: Who Is the Culprit?!
originalTitle: Kamen Raidâ × Supâ Sentai Supâ Hîrô Taihen: Hannin wa Dare da?!

title: Lost Angels
description: Lost Angels follows Jimmy, an unlikely FBI Operative, while he is immersed in the Lisanti Crime Ring. Jimmy operates under the wing, and in the shadow, of his older brother Special Agent Vincent Moretti. Vincent is fueled by the execution of his family, and he believes Lisanti may have been the trigger man. Jimmy is married to Donna, and together they have a beautiful daughter, Jamie. Donna and Jimmy's financial crisis has led them into a marital crisis, and Jimmy must finish his assignment before his family life, and possibly his own vanishes.

title: Kulinar
description: Felix Malinin lives in a small town. His friends and acquaintances regard think as a good person despite his sometimes unsocial and eccentric behavior and long absences due to frequent business trips. Felix's weakness is cooking, but he also has a secret known to only a few. Felix works for an investigation bureau attached to the Ministry of Internal Affairs, and his codename is Cook. His job involves undercover operations to collect information that may be of interest to the police. Capable of instantly transforming his appearance and behavior, Felix will do anything to get the information he requires. Giving each mission a culinary name, Felix approaches his assignments as if cooking a delicious new course, savouring and relishing their unique flavors.

title: Dark Prophet
description: DARK PROPHET is the story of gifted music student Dai Shepherd, who discovers top secrets hidden in the binary codes of songs, and then finds himself framed for his girlfriendâEUR(TM)s murder. To find her killer and save civilization, Dai must stop Black Box, the rogue Intel agency that planted the secrets, from triggering the cyber-intelligence takeover of the planet.

title: Borderline Coyotes
description: Three brothers work as Coyotes for the biggest Mob Boss in Los Angeles. This pack of Coyotes specializes in human smuggling: they bring people across the United States border from Mexico for a high price. But they are not the only Coyotes working for the Mob Boss. When rival crews get involved, this brotherly love is faced with betrayal, revenge, and greed.

title: YongYea
description: Yong Yea(YongYea) is a YouTuber who must take on the evil corporations such as Blizzard(Bobby Kotick) and EA(Andrew Wilson) in order to save the people of Gamerville.

title: Street Fighter X Tekken Vita
description: Characters from both the "Street Figther" and "Tekken" worlds collide in an epic battle of superpowers.

title: Turtl' Pavr!
description: The show is dedicated to one man's obsession with Teenage Mutant Ninja Turtles franchise (created by Kevin Eastman and Peter Laird), especially video games based on it. Suddenly gaining a cult status show quickly tried to do not only reviews, but also more cinematic scenes with original characters which had nothing to do with TMNT franchise.

title: Ozuma
description: In a desert world, the pirate crew Baldanos searches for the sand whale Ozuma.

title: Weird-O-Rama
description: "Weird-O-Rama" is a hosted horror movie show with Nik Havert as the horror host "Victor Von Psychotron" presenting movies on Michigan access TV Comcast Channel 99 in South Bend, Indiana, USA as well as Youtube.

title: Last Resort
description: Last Resort is tale of Jason Cobey, a retired hit-man who gave up the life for one with his daughter. But the past has a way of catching up to him. His daughter has been kidnap and he is forced to play a sick women's games to find her.

title: Hailmon Side
description: Hailmon Side is the chronicle of a good man plunged into the harsh underground world of a Los Angeles human trafficking ring. Forced by those elite, this man must reach out to the darkest corners of his sub-conscience in order to fulfill the endeavors put on him and repay his debt in order to save his only brother and the one he loves.

title: Khun Dech
description: It is a Thai hero series version. His name is Khun Dech. He wanted to protect Buddha images and ancient china-wares around ancient temple at Sukhothai Historical park from wicked persons.

title: Dai hao shi san chai
description: During the Anti-Japanese War, a group of highly trained female spies hold the key to defeating the enemies. Guo Chun Guang (Li Chao) is a highly trained spy for the Communist Party who goes undercover as a dentist in Shanghai to gather intelligence on the enemies. Gu Xue Feng (Li Zhu) becomes the new Shanghai stationmaster for the Kuomintang (KMT) military regime and is tasked with forming an all-female special force known as Code Thirteen.

title: Area 49
description: Special Agents Chan and Cooper investigate a Code 626.

title: Forever Mapa
description: Track Forever's trajectory by exploring Minecraft in an extreme and humanly impossible way.

title: Heroic Daze
description: In the corrupt city cf Nottywood, two brave, yet ridiculously unqualified, citizen's don their superhero alter egos and become "The JustUs League" to face the tyranny of Big Boss, Me-No Black, and The Firm.

title: Zonnentau
description: The lives of an ex-con, a mysterious historian, a female local journalist and an old man cross paths and intertwine in the most peculiar way, going way back into the past which neither of them reveal or is aware of.

title: Daihao shisan chai
description: During the Anti-Japanese War, a group of highly trained female spies hold the key to defeating the enemies. Guo Chun Guang (Li Chao) is a highly trained spy for the Communist Party who goes undercover as a dentist in Shanghai to gather intelligence on the enemies. Gu Xue Feng (Li Zhu) becomes the new Shanghai stationmaster for the Kuomintang (KMT) military regime and is tasked with forming an all-female special force known as Code Thirteen.

title: On Pace with Pastrana
description: The 29-year-old has broken nearly every bone in his body on his death-defying path to motorcross glory. Now, Travis is up against the biggest challenge of his professional career: to become a top competitor in NASCAR racing.

title: Another Hero
description: This is a story about Romain David, a super hero, who actually is a hero but not really a super one... He works officially as a night watchman in a hotel, but Romain's real aim is to get the world off Inferni, an evil multinational company. To handle his quest, Romain can only really on his two friends and roommates, Pascal and Fred. The three of them form the New Team and they won't give up their fight against Inferni Corporation !

title: Subject Zero
description: A group of friends set out on a mission to find the truth

title: Guris Guiris
description: Guris Guiris (a.k.a Michigan Patrol) is a fictional action-parody series, made in Spain, by Spaniards and in Spanish (language and accent), but telling a very American tale, full of stereotypes and references. It's a "No guts, no glory" tale from all the action USA buddy-cop movies in the 80s and 90s. Among twelve exciting episodes (plus one "Special Christmas"), we will know the story of a veteran cop, the rude and alcoholic Jack Hunter, and his companion, the young and handsome Lenny Lafiamma, buddies in arms in a criminal fictional Michigan D.C. They are consecrated law agents of The Michigan Patrol Police, a Corp that doesn't exist. And this Michigan city is plenty of dangerous villains, more than ever, in every street, in each corner. Jack Hunter lost his family years ago, so he drinks a lot; and Lenny Lafiamma is not be able to be a wife; he is the coolest, but the saddest too. Meanwhile, the evil Mendoza and his rapists, move the strings and rule the criminal suburbs. Mendoza is the Jack Hunter's worst nemesis, since he killed the young Timmy (Jack's eleven years old son) in the past. Now, he's leave the Federal Prison of Michigan, and he is furious, ready to execute the perfect revenge against Jack, killing his partner, stealing him everything and becoming the Evil Master King of Michigan. Now, the city is corrupted... on the edge, in the no turning back point. Only Jack Hunter and Lenny Lafiamma, with their guns, their guts and tons of testosterone, will be the only possible cure for the criminal plague.
